{"type": "article", "id": 23194, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-03T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 24298, "name": "KWAMBIO"}, {"id": 24299, "name": "Feltmark"}, {"id": 24300, "name": "Vélosophy"}, {"id": 24301, "name": "Behagen"}, {"id": 24302, "name": "Alexander Lervik"}, {"id": 24303, "name": "May Kukula"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110534ZhrQYT4Uz8nRXWsG.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Storm side table by Alexander Lervik &amp; Johanson</h2>\n<p>这是瑞典设计师 Alexander Lervik 在斯德哥尔摩家具展上展出的金属边桌，由一个圆弧框架和两个圆桌面组成，简单轻盈。上面的桌面可旋转 90 度，圆弧框架则充当了手提杆，因而也很方便提着它到处移动或者挂到墙边。具有北欧家具简洁优雅的特征。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121050k3Fbxzo0KXqWBEDe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64850427\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121050pNEg5OVTD2Qtf8s1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121050v0DwcBdlPOVtqiLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210512AKBOk3SsRQg5eaH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121051er9VclLAPDtwqbTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7542735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>3D printing by KWAMBIO</h2>\n<p>KWAMBIO 是纽约一家提供定制 3D 打印产品的网站，目前已联合 18 位设计师或设计组合提供超过 10 组产品。他们的设计不再是塑料一样的零件，而是具有审美价值的陶瓷物件或金属首饰。比如纽约设计师 Andrew Sack 带来的具有笔筒功能的花瓶，外形有点像古典园林中的梅花窗，具有装饰性。<a href=\"http://kwambio.com\">这里是网站的链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121052BYIsy4rP3KDNOS0V.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121052gB0pLfeVyIKFWaYA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121053NOBKcziG9u54Qq1e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121053zY5Kj93u2EXcTDge.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121053o20JmvBWMbu3eA5X.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Vellum Solar by Feltmark </h2>\n<p>这是一款可移动的灯，来自洛杉矶设计工作室 Feltmark。依靠安装在墙上的磁性支架，让它可贴在多个位置上。灯里含有太阳能电池板，所以不受插头和电线的限制，充电一天可供 6 个月的电，很适合放在走廊或卧室里成为一盏夜灯。而小巧的外形也可以让它带到旅游途中作为手电筒使用。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/byfeltmark/ellum-solar-light-different\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121054eGP4mYg5vBMSt10x.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121054cCHhEvLNSqk57Jyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210558TMI6vqpWmXFHwxy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121055OWHrev4ANXyP0a1B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121056OjJ6tGAgRkLNBXK2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>hotpot 热能锅 by May Kukula </h2>\n<p>这是一款用软木制成的热能锅，德国设计师 May Kukula 以节约资源为出发点设计。需要先在火炉上加热，但只需平时三分之一的时间。然后放在热能锅里，软木材质的保温性能让它保持持续蒸煮的状态，是降低能耗的方式。此外，浅色的软木和黑色的帖和白瓷搭配起来时，非常清新居家。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121056CNVyzI4lDBHcrE5m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121057shPB87e54mfLxEZq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121057eEnbF8L5tY02pI94.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121058dC4sSMmOIu2ytQWJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121058WnmjoHRZhD2GQIJC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Vélosophy bike</h2>\n<p>这是瑞典一家新的自行车品牌 Vélosophy 推出的两款的自行车，铝制框架结构纤细而轻盈，在轮胎、座位、扶手和踏板上点缀以明亮的颜色，让它显得非常时尚。自行车分为舒适型和运动型两款，舒适型的座位更宽，杠杆结构与地面水平，而运动型的杠杆斜向，座位更窄。另外可以选择两种开放式的车篮，都很有趣。售价 7200 瑞典克朗，<a href=\"http://buy.velosophy.cc\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121059QB84k0qG1De2YuUi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121059RYLqNFtBoE5uZaxz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121100raMkePIVdCShnful.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121100gBFvqs5aNAPrtbjd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121101fol9U813h4Mvzd6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121101z7vQohTLNZyGEBkD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Special Harvest Cafe Custepec by Behagen </h2>\n<p>这是一组很文艺的咖啡包装设计，墨西哥平面设计公司 Behagen 认为人们很愿意了解咖啡背后的故事，因而在包装上用小号字写了大量关于咖啡的起源和背景，不禁让人联想起那些爱喝咖啡的作家以及与咖啡有关的书。盒子是黑色的，尽管区别口味时也用了彩色的纸，但色调仍然偏灰，非常干净素雅。<a href=\"http://www.behagen.mx/special-harvest\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121102zuLSonWsYB18DElF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121102Qk2AOeu3ljBsfIp7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121103DwzxYhunc760CXGV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121103sYoBIWjRMybicLOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121104byltpJxToLF5MA1R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121104CZY3d0Q5i4Wy1HoI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}